(2, 89, 'Chris Williams', 'chriscommenttest@testcommnent.com', '', '62.193.157.37', '2018-10-05 11:12:36', '2018-10-05 11:12:36', 'Encyclopaedia galactica are creatures of the cosmos shores of the cosmic ocean. Cosmic ocean the sky calls to us consectetur cosmic ocean and billions upon billions upon billions upon billions upon.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(3, 89, 'Jane Smith', 'janecommentstest@testscomments.com', '', '62.193.157.37', '2018-10-05 11:14:17', '2018-10-05 11:14:17', 'As a patch of light consectetur adipisicing elit with pretty stories for which there\'s little good evidence rich in mystery?', 0, '1', '', '', 2, 0),
